<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.8">
<l>pattu nāḷuṅ kaṭanta viraṇṭānā</l>
<l>ḷetti caiyuñ cayamaraṅ kōṭittu</l>
<l>matta māmalai tāṅkiya maintaṉai</l>
<l>yuttā ṉañcey tukantaṉa rāyarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[On] the second day after ten days,</l>
<l>[they] erected a triumphal arch [on] all the cardinal points,</l>
<l>[and] having awakened the son who held up the mountain of the must-elephant,</l>
<l>the cowherds were pleased.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
